<p><br /></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Gene Editing system</p>
</blockquote>

<p>To overcome the uncontrolled nature of Cas9-gRNA complex cleavage activity in the current CRISPR/Cas9 system, several labs have designed ribozyme-induced gRNA release to achieve on-demand control of Cas9 activity.<br /></p>

